Doctor Swati Mourya,  
First of all heartly thanks to her,  she was the only Doctor Who made my son sit calm and do the procedure seamlessly.  Her handling of patients issues and Consultant is very precise and up-to the point **** ******** ********** 
Thank you once again. 
Strongly recommended.
